[
  {
    "scene": "TitleScene",
    "file": "01-title.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "歡迎來到誰讓他煉器的！第一章，第三集，丹爐修復。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "周墨正式加入煉器峰。長老交給他第一個任務：修復一座三百年歷史的丹爐。聽說這座丹爐有個小毛病——它會自己說話。而且脾氣比長老還大。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene1",
    "file": "02-content1.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "周墨，歡迎加入煉器峰。從今天起，你就是正式弟子了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "謝謝長老！請問我的第一個任務是什麼？"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "修丹爐。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "修丹爐？聽起來很簡單。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "不簡單。這座丹爐有三百年歷史，上一位負責修理的弟子，被它罵哭了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "丹爐......罵人？"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "它會說話。而且說的都是髒話。昨天它還在罵我們煉器峰的人連火都不會點。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "有意思。技術上來說，一個有意識的丹爐，這是一個高級智能終端。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你在說什麼？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "沒什麼。帶我去看看吧。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "到了，就是這座。你小心點，它最近心情不好。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "嗯......火焰陣法老化、溫控模組失靈、意識晶片過載。所以您生氣是因為沒有人維護您，對吧？"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "它好像......安靜了？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "問題的核心是使用者體驗。這座丹爐不是壞了，它是被忽視了三百年。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene2",
    "file": "03-content2.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "好了，我來幫您做一個全面的系統升級。火焰陣法重寫、自動控溫模組、還有——情緒管理系統。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "情緒管理系統？你要給丹爐做心理諮詢？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "準確地說，是情感交互界面。它生氣是因為沒有人聽它說話，所以我裝了一個傾聽模組。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "所以你修丹爐的方式是......陪它聊天？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "這只是其中一個功能。我還加了語音控制。現在只需要說一聲「請幫忙燒一下」就自動點火了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "倒是方便。不過......為什麼它在唱歌？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "哦，那是音樂播放功能。我覺得丹爐工作時也需要娛樂，不然多無聊。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你連丹爐的使用者體驗都考慮到了？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "當然。使用者體驗是產品設計的核心。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "好吧......不過它會不會在半夜自動開派對？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "不會。我加了定時休眠功能，它晚上會自動安靜下來。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "不錯不錯。看來你終於記得加停止鍵了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "嗯......不過我忘加音量控制了。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "OutroScene",
    "file": "04-outro.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
